>>>>> It takes around 3GIG of space and I've been editing it down to fit
>>>>> onto 3 CD`s.
>>>> 
>>>> Ah, Mpeg Layer 3 encoding, and it'll fit on one.

>>> Hmmm, but it wouldn`t play on a CD player then :)
>>> 

>> it will now, sony and someone else have released mp3 playing hardware
>> the commercial music market.....

> Does it play CDs? That would be a mega-ultra-wow thing...
> The first company to release a mp3 cd player would became bloody rich....

> Just imagine 13 albums packed into a single CD!!!

It doesn't play actual CD's, the idea is that you plug it into your PC
(spit, spit) and upload your selected MP3 files to the thing's own build in
memory.  I've seen a walkman type version, and there's also a HiFi version
as well.

