exceptional.  My best measured practice throw was about 143 meters (altho=
ugh
we measured them in yards).  We didn't always throw the grenades though. =
 In
some situations we were forced to get creative, and place grenades and sc=
oot
for cover.  C4 sachel charges they are not, but if they are all you have
they are better than nothing.  I guess with a 3 second fuse I wouldn't be=

trying any of that.  We used grenade launchers some also.  The poor mans
morter.


  Well, it's been fun, but of course off topic.  Still, as the crap fades=
 into
