hings
again.  If you want to jive privately with me on such matters feel free.
I am very interested in military tactics, history, weaponry and strategy =
from
all time periods.  Oh, and logistics too, believe it or not.  Some of the=

games I am working on will reflect these interests.


cacha later,

Donovan Reeve (bubby.lnk@ispi.net)



