> documentation?   How do you guys write the documentation?

We don't write documentation, didn't you know ? Anyway, if you're not upt=
o doing it by hand there is a utility called AGW (Amiga Guide Writer [Ori=
ginal name, don't you think ?]) on Aminet. It's not good, by a long shot,=
 but it'll do.


