@NODE "Mail_176" "Subject set, as ezmlm doesnt accept empty subject fields :-)"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Tue, 23 Mar 1999 03:48:14 +0000
From: amorel <amorel@xs4all.nl>
Date: Tue, 23 Mar 1999 04:45:55 +0500
Subject: Subject set, as ezmlm doesnt accept empty subject fields :-)

What code do you need to put in to be able to use your prog with version?

I do this:

goto skipthis
even
   dc.b "VER$: blah blah"
even
.skipthis:

This at least makes the info appear in a text viewer, if it reads in exe
files. Without the goto it crashes miserably :-)

What does dc.b do btw?

Regards

