>  Int rounds down, it sounds like he's trying to round to the nearest integer, 
> in which case you should do Print Str$(Int(value+0.5))

But even that won't work.   A number in the range 9.0 - 9.4999 will
round up to the "magic" range and STR$ will print it as "0".

