@ENDNODE
@NODE "Mail_204" "Shift Key"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Wed, 17 Mar 1999 15:06:52 +0000
From: Rick Hodger <rick.thehub@bigfoot.com>
Date: Wed, 17 Mar 1999 15:02:11 +0000
Organization: Pagan Software
Subject: Shift Key


I remember someone was looking for code to tell them if the shift key was
held down a few days ago? I forget who it was exactly, but here's what
you're looking for:

Function CheckForShift{}
  char.l=Peek.b($BFEC01) ; Keyboard register on CIA-A
  ;63/62 = Left Shift pressed/released
  ;61/60 = Right Shift pressed/released
  If char.l=60 OR char.l=61 OR char.l=62 OR char.l=63 Then ret=True
Function Return ret
End Function


-- 
