Hi BaH

On 29-Mar-99, BaH wrote:

> And to keep a little bit on topic...
> I vaguely remember someone was using a 'different' mod player/library in
> blitz for playing the likes of soundtracker/protracker mods.  I think it
> might have been Mr Burkey, though I may be wrong.  What is it, and where
