Ok, here's the breakdown of we'd *like* (and I stress 'like') to
release. What actually gets released may be different :

SuperTED		- 680x0 source code
Blitz2			- 680x0 source code (*)
REDBlitzLibs		- 680x0 source code
REDDebugger		- Blitz code
Support libraries	- 680x0 source code
REDDock			- Blitz code

