@NODE "Mail_284" "PowerBasic"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Tue, 16 Mar 1999 17:52:46 +0000
From: Roger Beausoleil <vision_fx@citenet.net>
Date: Thu, 22 Oct 1998 12:15:32 -0500
Subject: PowerBasic

Hi all,

We, Frederic Laboureur and Roger Beausoleil work on a new version of Blitz in
the background of the list since a long time now... And its name will be ..
PowerBasic!

We splited the project in parts to do each other. And I can say that we will
be ready for a 68000 beta version pretty soon and, if the result are good as
we espected... the upgrade for PPC will come few time after.

For my Part:
