 my understanding that if you use AREXX, you must keep AREXX syntax at al=
l times, with message ports you can send any tosh you feel like (For exam=
ple a screendump or something). I dunno if you can do this with AREXX. Of=
fcourse, once again, since I'm rather crap at OS progamming, I could be m=
istaken.


