Date: Mon, 08 Mar 1999 11:24:36 +0000
From: stocksjames <stocksjames@KNOCK.co.uk>
Organization: Our Lady & St. Patrick's College, Knock
	Julie Bradley <JulieB@IMRNI.COM>,
	Gordon Turnbull <gturnbull@oblique-design.demon.co.uk>,
	Blitz Users <blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie>,
	Bernie Stocks <b.stocks@ulst.ac.uk>
Subject: Nu Old Skool Blaster
Encoding: 7bit

A small shoot 'em up I wrote in Blitz is now available-

http://stocksy.future.easyspace.com/stuff.htm

THIS IS NOT THE GAME I WANT BETA-TESTED!!! That one still isn't
finished...

It's quite simple (two days to write from scratch), but is good fun.
There may be problems getting it off my site- Netscape treats it as
text, and reaches an EOF char about 2k in. Mail me if you have problems.

If anyone likes this game, tell me, and I might redo it properly.
Bug reports also welcome, though bear in mind I've been quite lazy (e.g.
holding the mouse button to quit)

Send me your best scores, and enjoy!!!!

	James

