    Hello to all my friends!

Well I've just gotten a new email adress which is andy.h@telia.com
please update your email adress books to include this one instead
of the old one (andy@bjuv.mail.telia.com), since all emails sent to the
old email adress (andy@bjuv.mail.telia.com) wont reach me.

This is due to an error made by my ISP (internet supplier) when I was
in the proccess of changing my account with them from one to another
(cheeper one, hehe =). In this proccess the old email address
(andy@bjuv.mail.telia.com) was lost, so I had to register the new email
andh.h@telia.com inorder to be able to send and recieive emails.

I REPEAT! DO NOT USE andy@bjuv.mail.telia.com ANYMORE, SINCE
IT'S OUT OF ORDER. PLESE REFER TO USING andh.h@telia.com
INSTEAD, SINCE IT'S MY NEW EMAIL ADRESS AND IT SHOULD BE
USED AT ALL TIMES, WHEN YOU WISH TO SEND ME ANY EMAILS!

For those who have a hard time understanding english, I appologise, but
the people in my contact list are spread all over the world, I decided to
write
it in english to reach all of you, without having to write multiple copies
in
diffrent languages.

One last time. Use andy.h@telia.com as the email adress when you wish
to contact me, since my old email account has been terminated.

Kindest regards,

Andreas




