@NODE "Mail_349" "My own tuppence worth"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Sat, 13 Mar 1999 14:41:43 +0000
From: "Jes" <jes@cosmothecat.freeserve.co.uk>
Subject: My own tuppence worth
