Hi all,

I was trying out theUI class, TextEditor.mcc in Blitz today when I finally
reached a point where it continually crashed! ;(

Seems that the objects pointer is causing the error, I need this for the
scrollbar so I use

    MUINewObject 1,"ScrollBar.mui",0
    slid.l=MUIObjLoc(1)

Then continue with the program, which is attached. If I comment out the
AddTag bit that attaches it to the TextEditor, it works fine, if I leave it
in it crashes when either exiting or moving the slider up and down ;(

