From: Sami =?iso-8859-1?Q?N=E4=E4t=E4nen?= <sami.naatanen@dlc.fi>
Date: Wed, 03 Mar 1999 22:42:37 +0300
Subject: MP3 Walkmans Vs. MiniDisc VERY of TOPIC
Encoding: quoted-printable

On 03-Mar-99, Mikkel L=F8kke wrote.

>  On 03-Mar-99, Andreas H=E5kansson wrote:
>  =

>  >> RH> It doesn't play actual CD's, the idea is that you plug it into
your PC
