own
>  >> RH> build in memory.  I've seen a walkman type version, and there's=

also a
>  >> RH> HiFiversion as well.
>  >> Are you talking about the Diamond Rio.....it has 32Mb of internal
memory to
>  >> hold 7 tracks. These can be changed by uploading MP3 files from you=
r
PC into
>  >> it. The whole unit is smaller than a cigarette packet and runs from=

one AA
>  >> battery.
>  >> Neat kit, but at over 180 GBP, it's not cheap.
>  =

