That isn't the problem, the problem is that you have to write two seperate
engines that can understand the possible error codes for both FTP and
HTTP.

> As for the gui, I figure we could have a mui and non mui interface...if a
> couple of people did similar ones, then it`s upto the user to choose.

> Rick Hodger claims to have done this already...I`m not sure if he
