> for anyones software. If this program is already available..then there
> isn`t too much point in doing another one.

I have done, www.thehub.u-net.com under the downloads sections, it's called
CSUpdate.  I'm trying to add HTTP1.1 to it, but it's a right pain cause the
server always sends wee messages like the last time the file was altered
etc.

It doesn't support FTP however, which would be a nice thing to add. :)

