ftp/http is better. And the fact that aminet isn`t likely to move..so when
you make some software, and use aminet as the update check..it will always
be there...unlike any old web address (which seem to dissapear more often
that not!)...btw...you don`t need to go through all that to get the info on
a file in ftp...the best thing to do is....

