> Thank you,
I wont work for anything but floppy that way=2E This is because blitz
mode kills the O/S from running and that is what you nead=2E  Of couse
you could jump back and forth from blitz mode to Amiga mode=2E  That
would just stop all action for short while=2E

Programing support of HD is _lot_ hard work and probley wont work with
3=2E5 when it comes out=2E=20=20
Then is so easy to write it for floppy then?
Well it isn't realy but every one has same type of floppy drive (Bar
non Commodore systems) same soure will work on any floppy drive=2E  But
I wouldn't trust that such system will work in the future=2E  I wouldn't
get to worred about future systems as O/S for Version 5 is going to be
nothing like what we have now, as I understand it=2E
