Hello Jochen.

On 12-Mar-99, Jochen Heizmann wrote:

> Is it possible to play IFF Animations using Blitz Basic direct from Dis=
c (if
> possible using the Blitz Mode). So that I can play IFF Anims, that does=
n't
> fit in memory.

First of all, in Blitz mode ou don't have I/O access, second, to my knowl=
edge there is no way using standard Blitz commands to stream video from a=
 device...


