@NODE "Mail_543" "Help! i need CD32 PAD information"
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Tue, 30 Mar 1999 19:33:34 +0100
From: Christian Uceda <copysoft@mx3.redestb.es>
Date: Tue, 30 Mar 1999 20:25:02 +0100
Importance: High
Organization: CSS Ltd.
Subject: Help! i need CD32 PAD information

Hello blitzers

I need information on how the CD32 Pad works...

I know how a joystick with  two button works but i haven't any idea on how
the others button in the cd32 pad works...

can any one help me?????

Hellos From Spain



-- 
Christian Uceda Fernandez.
