@NODE "Mail_546" "Help with loading codes from BUM's...."
 for scott@online.u-net.com; Tue, 23 Mar 1999 07:15:28 +0000
From: Andrew Bruno <abruno@zeta.org.au>
Date: Sun, 21 Mar 1999 16:16:27 +1000
Subject: Help with loading codes from BUM's....

Hi,

Well, as many of you may now know:  I have got blitz working.  And I am
happy!

I decided to look at a few of the examples off the bum's, but often when I
load a program (appended either .bb or .bb2) I get an error:  Can't load
resident".

Hey, I live here!  ;)

But seriously, I take it that there is a file missing.

How do I avert this problem?  Or better:  Fix it?

Thanks!


Cya!
-- 
