Hi Tony

On 10-Mar-99, Tony Rolfe wrote:
> Hi,
> 
> Is there any way to tell which gadget (if any) has the cursor in it?

When the GTstringGadget is selected (cursor in it) you will get a GadgetDown
message ($20)

When it is exited, you get GadgetUp ($40)

