Subject: GTListViews
Encoding: quoted-printable

Hi Blitzers,

I'd like to know why the following code causes a GURU (#$80000003) on 680=
00/68010 machines (A500/A600):

-------------------

; It needs the amigalibs.res file

  SetErr
    DisplayBeep_ 0
    End
  End SetErr

  WBStartup

  NoCli

  NEWTYPE .gtlv
    a.w
    Name$
  End NEWTYPE

  Dim List MemLabel.gtlv(10)

  ClearList MemLabel()
  For m.l=3D1 To 10
    AddItem MemLabel():MemLabel()\Name=3DStr$(m)
  Next

  FindScreen 0

  GTTags #GTLV_ShowSelected,0
  GTListView 2,51,0,0,100,100,"",0,MemLabel()
  GTSetAttrs 2,51,#GTLV_Selected,3
  AddIDCMP $600010
  WindowTags 2,$e,"",#WA_Left,20,#WA_Top,20,#WA_InnerWidth,150,#WA_InnerH=
eight,150
  WTitle "Window","Test"
  AttachGTList 2,2

  Repeat
    ev.l=3DWaitEvent
  Until ev=3D$200

  End

-------------------

The problem seems to be in one of the following lines (or both):

  GTTags #GTLV_ShowSelected,0

  GTSetAttrs 2,51,#GTLV_Selected,3


Could you please help me?




-- =

Best regards,

Luca.

