On the 28th Feb 1999, Loki asked:

>   Anyone know how to use: #GTTX_Justification in blitz to
>centre the text in the gadget? What the tag value is?
>
>Any help would be appreciated, ta :)
>byeee

#GTTX_Justification = $80080074

Left = 0
Right = 1
Centre = 2

Hope that helps.


