Hya Anton

>#> First of all the Voodoo2 is a 3D accelerator and will do nothing for
>#> your bitmap rotation.
> 
>   Yeah, I was just being sarcastic really :-)

But not entirelly. If you use the Voodoo and texture map you car onto
a polygon, you can now rotate the polygon at high speed, or at least
as fast as the card can handle. You can even do Zoom In/Out very
easilly. It seems weird to use 3D to do 2D stuff but if it
works..............

Cya

Silver
aka Nuno Trancoso


