Oh, Curt, you should know by now, everything you ever wanted is in my
amazing StatsFuncs file ;)

Here's the replacements :

Statement GoPAL {}
  MOVE #32,$dff1dc
End Statement

Statement GoNTSC {}
  MOVE #0,$dff1dc
End Statement

Just stick 'em at the top of your code, and call them by doing :

GoPAL {}

or

GoNTSC {}

 
