 boundary="------------1DB6DF2BEAAA3B1723D43753"

This is a multi-part message in MIME format.
--------------1DB6DF2BEAAA3B1723D43753
Encoding: 7bit

Anton Reinauer wrote:
> 
> On 16-Mar-99, BlokeBlock wrote:
> 
> > ... why not use StoneCracker instead? Way better than CrunchMania AND
> > I know how it works! :)
> >
